Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.40,0:01:53.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,令千金逸子小姐在我們手中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.00,0:01:57.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們的目的\N不是令千金小姐的命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.60,0:02:04.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果您不給予我們滿意答覆\N我們也只好殺生了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.18,0:02:09.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希望令千金平安的話\N就答應我們要求吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.98,0:02:12.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請以此為優先
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.16,0:02:30.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第八十一話\N紅葵的陰謀\N攻擊海舟的幕末生靈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.92,0:02:45.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎樣 有找到逸子嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.75,0:02:47.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行 找不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.65,0:02:49.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這附近都找過了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.13,0:02:54.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大五郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.06,0:02:58.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她也沒去豆腐店
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.27,0:03:01.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是 她去哪裏了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.00,0:03:04.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要是小姐發生萬一的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.04,0:03:08.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,先冷靜下來啦 她可能回家了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.28,0:03:11.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是要回家也該先說一聲啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.78,0:03:15.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我再去找一遍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.65,0:03:19.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,慢著 你這樣\N漫無目標亂跑沒用的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.02,0:03:21.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓腦袋冷靜下來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.49,0:03:23.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.72,0:03:25.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對了 劍心呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.46,0:03:27.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他還沒回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.83,0:03:29.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知道到哪裏找人去了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.10,0:04:08.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,應該戰鬥到底
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.67,0:04:10.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不 這個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.60,0:04:13.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當前第一要務\N應該是找出談和之道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.01,0:04:16.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,事到如今你以為可能嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.21,0:04:19.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對了 向法國請求援軍怎樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.91,0:04:23.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可能 這是最愚蠢的行為
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.35,0:04:27.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼 你說我是愚人嗎\N不可原諒！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.49,0:04:31.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,兩位冷靜 現在別吵了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.42,0:04:35.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,眼前應該是考慮\N怎樣處理逼近的薩長軍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.07,0:04:41.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,勝海舟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.17,0:04:41.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.97,0:04:47.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,江戶市的情況怎樣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.27,0:04:52.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是 昨夜開始\N薩長軍進攻的消息傳來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.31,0:04:57.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,街道都被避難的人潮\N擠得水洩不通
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.02,0:05:03.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有很多人想經由海路\N逃離江戶 碼頭一片混亂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.19,0:05:07.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,德川的時代要結束了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.83,0:05:13.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓事態發展成今天這局面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.73,0:05:15.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全是我的錯誤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.87,0:05:18.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我願接受任何責難
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.34,0:05:21.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是我不能\N讓江戶的人民捲入戰火
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.94,0:05:24.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,使無辜的人們流血犧牲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.61,0:05:26.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,將軍大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.15,0:05:30.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算我會沒命也無妨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.45,0:05:38.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是…小的知道將軍的覺悟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.39,0:05:42.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,既然這樣 小的賭上性命\N也要完成任務
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.16,0:05:45.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜託你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.32,0:06:06.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,勝先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.59,0:06:10.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是你啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.67,0:06:24.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天凌晨二點\N在品川兩源寺等你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.80,0:06:25.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,紅葵筆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.81,0:06:30.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起 辜負您的委託了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.74,0:06:33.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不 是我太天真了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.58,0:06:35.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是 他們是怎麼找到的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.42,0:06:41.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,政府還以為\N我把那些錢交給西鄉隆盛了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.62,0:06:44.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這麼說 寶藏的傳聞是真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.49,0:06:45.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,恩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.09,0:06:49.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是相信你才告訴你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.56,0:06:53.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這件事\N連我的徒弟和逸子都不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.47,0:06:55.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,應該不會洩露的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.74,0:07:02.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總之那些錢\N是我代為保管的重要東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.74,0:07:04.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,將軍的委託呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.31,0:07:07.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是說德川慶喜公爵嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.38,0:07:08.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.48,0:07:10.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為何要把財寶藏起來？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.78,0:07:12.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.05,0:07:14.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果無血開城時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.45,0:07:18.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓薩長軍把巨款沒收掉\N你想事態會變成怎樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.06,0:07:23.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等於送他們大筆錢拿去打仗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.57,0:07:29.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個時代潮流非常激烈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.10,0:07:31.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,任何人都被捲入
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.30,0:07:34.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不抓穩一點\N誰知道會被衝到什麼地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.31,0:07:40.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我還有我該做的事呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.32,0:07:51.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,自從那位大人把將軍位\N還給天皇以後已經十年了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.53,0:08:04.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,至今還被害怕\N德川力量的明治政府軟禁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.64,0:08:08.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,處於身份不明的狀態
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.34,0:08:13.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想讓拯救江戶人民\N免於戰火的大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.71,0:08:16.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,早日跟政府和解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.05,0:08:18.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在那一天來到之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.48,0:08:21.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不會讓寶藏外流的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.35,0:08:25.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是我身為幕府臣子\N勝海舟的最後工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.89,0:08:28.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.90,0:08:35.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,您打算一個人去嗎\N也讓我隨行吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.64,0:08:38.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不 我一個人去就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.27,0:08:43.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,歸根究底錯是我犯下的\N我不能把你捲進來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.31,0:08:45.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看你那把刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.98,0:08:50.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我就瞭解你在維新時代\N是怎樣活下來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.75,0:08:53.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,勝先生 幕末時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.25,0:08:57.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那把劍你連護衛自己時\N都不肯拔出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.16,0:09:00.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想是因為你的理想\N就封印在今夜的封印裏吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.43,0:09:04.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這只是明知天真\N卻想堅持到底的一口氣罷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.93,0:09:09.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好了 還有一點時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.04,0:09:12.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,您到底打算怎樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.21,0:09:16.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,放心吧 我不打算去送死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.58,0:09:20.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也不想把錢交出去\N也不會讓逸子死掉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.98,0:09:23.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再見了 謝謝你專程過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.38,0:09:24.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哪裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.65,0:09:29.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對了 這件事你別告訴大五郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.06,0:09:32.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他雖然膽小但若知道此事\N誰曉得會幹出什麼呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.69,0:09:35.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓他死於一時意氣用事\N就太可惜了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.13,0:09:39.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,勝先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.91,0:09:49.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂 那條路是回神谷道場的反方向哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.98,0:09:51.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左之助！還有大家！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.94,0:09:55.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心 你要來這裏的話\N可以先說一聲的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.51,0:09:56.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,害人家為你擔心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.88,0:09:59.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請問逸子小姐呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.45,0:10:01.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她有回家嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.73,0:10:09.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到底怎樣了 逸子小姐\N是不是發生事情了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.60,0:10:12.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大五郎 這裏不方便講
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.57,0:10:15.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們換個地方\N我再慢慢跟你說明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.88,0:10:29.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被綁架了？！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.45,0:10:31.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼這樣 為何逸子會被…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.05,0:10:38.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真沒用 你振作一點吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.06,0:10:39.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.73,0:10:41.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不像話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.66,0:10:46.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,勝先生叫我別告訴你的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.43,0:10:49.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為我不可靠是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.20,0:10:53.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是的 他是為了你好呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.24,0:10:58.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心 總之我們得救出逸子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.24,0:10:59.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快去報警啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.01,0:11:02.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小姐 現在不好哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.48,0:11:05.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼 我們應該早一點…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.79,0:11:08.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,勝海舟\N不是成為政府眼中釘嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.89,0:11:13.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,事關德川的寶藏 事情複雜了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.29,0:11:18.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,勝先生說要一個人去\N就是考慮到這一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.50,0:11:20.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說什麼 老師一個人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.50,0:11:26.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他可能是想 必要時\N用自己一人的生命來負責
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.01,0:11:29.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼這樣…怎麼這樣…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.64,0:11:33.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對了 找警察不行的話\N可以去找鐵馬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.51,0:11:37.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是那個人是政府官員啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.25,0:11:39.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比找警察更糟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.22,0:11:44.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不 鐵馬過去\N一直保護老師不受政府迫害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.49,0:11:46.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這次一定也能幫上忙的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.01,0:12:09.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,逸子啊 原諒我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.62,0:12:16.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鐵馬一定有辦法擺平這件事\N又不驚動到政府的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.29,0:12:21.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我就是不想\N欠那男人一個人情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.09,0:12:23.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在不是說那種話的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.90,0:12:25.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你真的認為可以嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.60,0:12:30.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我說 你把解救逸子的事\N交給別人可以嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.20,0:12:32.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.04,0:12:43.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,凌晨兩點在品川見面嗎\N現在不走會趕不上的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.22,0:12:44.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼辦 劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.42,0:12:47.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,勝先生叫我別去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.82,0:12:52.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以你的個性\N不可能乖乖答應吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.16,0:12:57.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我早就有所覺悟\N出手幫忙以後再挨罵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.80,0:12:59.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我就說應該這樣子嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.97,0:13:02.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當然 我也要一起去哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.84,0:13:04.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看來我也阻止不了你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.67,0:13:06.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對啊 你挺瞭解的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.81,0:13:08.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大五郎你在道場等著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.24,0:13:10.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也要去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.28,0:13:12.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,誰叫逸子常做好吃的飯\N給大家吃呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.95,0:13:15.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼 你還分得出好壞啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.05,0:13:16.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你沒資格說我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.38,0:13:18.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說什麼 你說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.88,0:13:23.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊…我也要 我也要去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.36,0:13:28.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂 你一起去不好啦\N到時會有大混戰的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.36,0:13:31.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即使如此\N即使如此我還是要去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.76,0:13:33.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想要救逸子小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.37,0:13:35.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大五郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.40,0:13:43.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不像鐵馬一樣\N有地位又劍術高明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.54,0:13:44.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大五郎…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.34,0:13:47.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我自己都覺得慚愧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.51,0:13:49.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,逸子有危險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.38,0:13:52.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我卻想依賴鐵馬\N不敢馬上趕去救人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.92,0:13:56.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我去了…大概也是累贅吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.09,0:14:06.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,神谷活心流是活人劍\N是保護人的劍呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.67,0:14:09.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是我的門生不是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.30,0:14:10.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,絕對沒問題的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.67,0:14:11.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.71,0:14:14.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,走吧 一起去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.27,0:14:15.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去保護逸子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.64,0:14:18.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.08,0:14:22.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就這麼說定\N我們沒時間在這裏浪費了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.92,0:14:25.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心 你在這裏等著\N我去做準備
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.82,0:14:28.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也是 走了 大五郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.19,0:14:28.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.26,0:14:36.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今夜真是愉快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.43,0:14:39.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不用客氣\N盡量喝吧 大久保鐵馬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.43,0:14:40.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是 那我不客氣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.64,0:14:46.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你也挺會喝酒的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.81,0:14:48.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對了 勝大人還好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.94,0:14:50.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是 托福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.38,0:14:52.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.41,0:14:57.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了西鄉的軍需事件\N大人一定搞得心力交瘁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.28,0:14:58.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,辛苦你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.25,0:15:03.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不敢 那時候多虧您的照顧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.36,0:15:05.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哪裏哪裏 那沒什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.99,0:15:09.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那件事我也認為是誤會呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.10,0:15:12.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,勝大人是了不起的人物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.36,0:15:17.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你能拜那種人為師\N是你的幸福呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.20,0:15:17.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.91,0:15:24.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有你這麼優秀的年輕人\N在政府的中樞工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.84,0:15:30.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,日本會更加富裕\N我們都對你期望很大哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.08,0:15:33.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我會日以繼夜求進步\N以不辜負您的期望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.99,0:15:38.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要你有那意思\N我隨時都會替你講話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.69,0:15:41.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好早日讓那一天實現
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.89,0:15:44.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要快一點 是嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.16,0:15:48.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你也漸漸學會了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.57,0:15:50.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是愉快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.08,0:15:59.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂 酒啊 再拿酒來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.52,0:16:04.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大五郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.65,0:16:06.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大五郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.93,0:16:16.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大五郎真是的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.20,0:16:17.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在這裏睡覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.73,0:16:23.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒辦法嘛 昨晚他又讀到很晚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.87,0:16:25.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊 鐵馬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.44,0:16:26.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打擾了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.27,0:16:29.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大五郎熱心讀書是不錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.01,0:16:32.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是不知\N他能不能幫上老師的忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.71,0:16:34.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我很懷疑哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.51,0:16:38.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒關係的 看到他的表情\N我的心情就平靜下來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.88,0:16:41.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這表示\N現在是天下太平的好時代呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.95,0:16:43.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我很高興
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.69,0:16:48.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,時代變化可以讓你們年輕人\N自由選擇生活方式的好時代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.53,0:16:53.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想到這點\N我就覺得我做的事並不是白廢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.50,0:16:56.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爸爸\N你老說這種話會老得很快的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.97,0:17:00.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爸爸你應該\N永遠保持健康活力的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.81,0:17:02.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是說 老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.57,0:17:07.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不用你們擔心 我會很長壽的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.62,0:17:12.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大五郎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.15,0:17:14.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你醒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.05,0:17:16.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是誰 這是哪裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.52,0:17:23.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,紅葵 說了你也不會瞭解\N這裏是品川的某座寺廟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.76,0:17:25.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼我會在這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.13,0:17:29.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你乖乖聽話就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.80,0:17:33.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不想殺害一個弱女子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.24,0:17:36.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等事情辦完就放你回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.28,0:17:38.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,事情？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.11,0:17:41.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你父親 勝海舟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.31,0:17:43.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你想對父親做什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.65,0:17:44.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,殺他！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.09,0:17:55.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在這裏的人\N都是過去為幕府工作的臣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.26,0:17:59.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如今他失去活著的希望\N變成這個模樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.16,0:18:04.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們不知忍受\N多少痛苦活下來…在維新之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.47,0:18:10.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,地位、名譽、住的家\N全部被奪走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.41,0:18:17.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,流浪到陌生的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.58,0:18:21.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在絕望之中還一一失去了家人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.74,0:18:44.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是誰讓世界變成這樣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.59,0:19:00.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,連戰鬥的機會都不給我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.50,0:19:04.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就這樣投降的傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.03,0:19:06.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你想說這都是家父害的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.90,0:19:09.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,家父為了救大家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.57,0:19:11.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓江戶免於戰火…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.77,0:19:15.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯 江戶被守住了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.27,0:19:20.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為那是慶喜將軍的決定\N我才聽從了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.61,0:19:22.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼為什麼…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.38,0:19:26.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有個人告訴我真相
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.55,0:19:31.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這一切都是\N勝海舟為了私慾所做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.42,0:19:35.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了保護自身安全\N獨佔德川家的龐大財產
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.26,0:19:39.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他才欺騙慶喜公爵\N促使公爵決定投降
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.87,0:19:42.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是謊言！是那個人胡說！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.47,0:19:46.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼\N為何勝海舟有德川的寶藏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.94,0:19:48.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是事實
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.44,0:19:50.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明治政府\N也注意到這點而展開行動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.61,0:19:52.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼這樣…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.78,0:19:56.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了幕末的恥辱\N和我們的未來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.18,0:19:58.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不能讓勝海舟活著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.72,0:20:00.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的目的到底是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.45,0:20:01.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,維新成功了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.02,0:20:04.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當然也能反過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.19,0:20:06.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,反過來？什麼意思？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.36,0:20:10.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,殺死勝海舟以後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.36,0:20:14.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要利用德川的寶藏\N來掀起革命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.34,0:20:22.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以慶喜公爵為盟主\N復興幕府
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.74,0:20:28.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這就是我們紅葵的目的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.42,0:20:33.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,時間差不多到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.73,0:21:23.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼辦 要一口氣衝進去嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.24,0:21:26.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在講什麼啊\N我們連敵人人數都不知
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.71,0:21:28.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你怕嗎 禰彥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.27,0:21:29.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.47,0:21:31.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,安靜 會被發現的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.88,0:21:33.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,勝先生還沒到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.81,0:21:36.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們先確認逸子的位置吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.32,0:21:43.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:44.92,0:21:47.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,冷靜下來 一定沒問題的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.73,0:21:49.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:05.74,0:22:06.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大五郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:06.34,0:22:06.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左之助
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:07.88,0:22:09.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,逸子小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:09.92,0:22:11.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快回來 大五郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.08,0:22:12.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:12.45,0:22:13.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大五郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:14.32,0:22:15.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,住手
